sources.title: Thanasis Veggos Voifeia! in "O Veggos Thaneros Prakathr 000" (1967)
sources.description: Vengos studies in a secret agents' academy, dreaming of becoming a great spy like 007. Unfortunately, he can't do anything right, so he wreaks havoc during his final exams.
